text: Yvonne Hasler is a former heptathlete and sprinter from Liechtenstein. Yvonne competed in the women's 200 metres at the 1988 Summer Olympics. She was born on October 13, 1968.Yvonne Hasler == References == Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Liechtenstein people Category:Sprinters
